{"tid":371550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港斷水斷電 24小時⋯","createTime":"2017-08-23T18:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T15:55:45.000Z","uid":139139,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03846dfc2433ec77db4f28d1651e0b8389793e26","tid":371550,"uid":139139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"我諗暴動都似，冇cctv 好似無法無天咁。<br />\n大把強姦犯丶夫目前犯現身，香港人啲獸性即刻出哂黎。<br />\n打刧錶行，入金鋪行個圈，搶iPhone 冇記認。<br />\n<br />\n如果有改裝bb彈槍，入鐵彈，加支電槍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放火燒立法會，打幾個警察，搶兩支炮，應該好多人去殺啲議員，國定殺戮日咁樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一日足夠香港亂，一星期可以返番春秋戰國。<br />\n女權馬上收皮，男人天下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔敢出街，你地第一樣野應該做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046d680f9f7f0a8d3fd60e41004d33425e262e5e","tid":371550,"uid":838,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:13:26.000Z","msg":"返工"},{"pid":"19f222c6a31cd03a2c024d3c552263c66ff8e782","tid":371550,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:14:21.000Z","msg":"不安"},{"pid":"971413304a3a3a6d2f733eddc49a1ceae816d086","tid":371550,"uid":114584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不安</blockquote><br />\n如果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ba022f5f318057670bb44c6bd111bd20db6f6d","tid":371550,"uid":27605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:23:26.000Z","msg":"你炮都無枝 講經咩 <br />\n果陣實成街警察<br />\n你隨地吐啖口水都比人拉返去"},{"pid":"056c62ac7c7f409cd351b97a92434449558ec075","tid":371550,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"香港人梗係擔心返唔到工做唔到野啦<br />\n驚緊有返水電嗰陣要一次過趕返起之前做唔到嘅野"},{"pid":"5d28904e609058f021d72cd416eaba0fc537c288","tid":371550,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你炮都無枝 講經咩 <br />\n果陣實成街警察<br />\n你隨地吐啖口水都比人拉返去</blockquote><br />\n無電 成街警察 你估有冇人入警局呀啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa27216e2adacd23e269c149a84ed5f0df1e9ab","tid":371550,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"冇電咁我點搭地鐵返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起都驚"},{"pid":"b1ec2396d8d9a07554537192b33bcab53cc9bad1","tid":371550,"uid":139139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你炮都無枝 講經咩 <br />\n果陣實成街警察<br />\n你隨地吐啖口水都比人拉返去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加州大地震咁，d人搶電視又iPhone 。<br />\n冇電冇完美通訊，組織好困難。<br />\n你睇下澳門咁細，而家咪打刧人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我留係家中等消息算！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fe87408d546c92b632b80770f903d17432ddf7","tid":371550,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工</blockquote><br />\n斷工24小時先最得人驚"},{"pid":"69ef99d6995ebe1a76f8a4910b2a04f391b32ebe","tid":371550,"uid":139139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:43:21.000Z","msg":"補圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/024305_02275a825dde2eb49277eb514153b54c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F024305_02275a825dde2eb49277eb514153b54c.jpg&h=36d96acc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/024306_d6f67f564c5fb080be690a5ae24b535d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F024306_d6f67f564c5fb080be690a5ae24b535d.jpg&h=902695e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/024306_959fad4336b256a401ae0a659ccb0be8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://